The e2m.live app lets a user:
- Broadcast Sessions
- Join Live Video Round tables
- Conduct Live Streaming of Pre-Recorded Video
- View Agenda, Speakers, Session and Attendee Info.
- Use Audience Response solutions like 1:1 messaging,Group Messaging and Live Q&A
- Visit Virtual Exhibitor Booths,sign up for digital sales & marketing collateral, Schedule call back and even live video chat with exhibitor sales personnel.


Features of the app :

- Live Video Roundtable
- Live Session Broadcast
- Simulated Live for Pre-Recorded Video
- On-Demand Session Videos
- Virtual Trade-show and Exhibitor Pavilion
- User Registration
- 1:1 Video with Attendees and Exhibitors
